# WatermelonDB / SQLite local databases
# (native builds/emulator runs can spit these out at the project root
# or in test artifacts — you never want a paramedic's local DB in git)
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-journal
*.sqlite-wal
*.sqlite-shm
*.db

